column2: SELECT TOP # g.source_id, g.ra as ra_gaia, g.ra_error, g.dec as dec_gaia, g.dec_error, g.pmra, g.pmra_error, g.pmdec, g.pmdec_error, g.parallax, g.parallax_error, g.parallax_over_error, g.phot_g_mean_flux_over_error, g.phot_g_mean_mag, g.phot_bp_mean_flux_over_error, g.phot_bp_mean_mag, g.phot_rp_mean_flux_over_error, g.phot_rp_mean_mag, g.bp_rp, g.absmag_g, n.objid, n.distance, o.ra AS ra_SDSS, o.dec AS dec_sdss INTO MyDB.bitch_please FROM MyDB.gaia_WD_only AS g CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNeareastObjEq (g.ra, g.dec, #) AS n JOIN PhotoObj AS o ON n.objid = o.objid
